{"messages": [{"type": "human", "data": {"content": "I've been planning this trip for WEEKS and every time I ask for flight options from London to Cape Town you give me the same vague nonsense. This tool is a complete waste of time.", "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "human", "name": null, "id": null, "example": false}}, {"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "I'm truly sorry to hear that your experience hasn't been as helpful as it should be. Let's make sure we get you the information you need this time. 

Cape Town is a city that captivates with its stunning landscapes, from the iconic Table Mountain to the vibrant V&A Waterfront. It's a place where nature and culture blend seamlessly, offering experiences that are both breathtaking and enriching.

Could you let me know your preferred travel dates and how many passengers will be traveling? This way, I can provide you with specific flight options that suit your plans.", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 109, "prompt_tokens": 1961, "total_tokens": 2070, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": 0, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 0, "rejected_prediction_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 1920}}, "model_name": "gpt-4o-2024-08-06", "system_fingerprint": "fp_395c203642", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "run--019e102d-7bfc-77d1-a9db-8ee46d1df61c-0", "example": false, "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 1961, "output_tokens": 109, "total_tokens": 2070, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 1920}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 0}}}}]}

